The '''Kalindan Deep Space Fleet''' was the navy commanded by the monarchs of the [[Kalinda system/Legends|Kalinda system]]. The fleet engaged elements of the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Battle of Kalinda]]. The fighting cost both sides numerous assets and casualties, which allowed a fleet from the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] to land an [[Enforcer Battle Group]] and take control of twenty-five percent of the planet.

==Behind the scenes==
In the [[Twin Stars of Kira (sourcebook)|''Twin Stars of Kira'']], the Kalindan Deep Space Fleet is mistakenly referred to as the "Kalidean Deep Space Fleet."

